---
import ServiceDetailLayout from "../../layouts/ServiceLayoutDetails.astro";
import { SERVICES } from "../../utils/constants";

const celebrityService = SERVICES.find(
  (service) => service.slug === "celebrity"
);

// Additional metadata specifically for Celebrity service
const serviceMetadata = {
  metaDescription:
    "Exclusive studio rental for celebrities and public figures in Nagpur. Private venue, VIP amenities, and premium sets at Pixxel City Studio.",
  ogImage:
    "https://images.pexels.com/photos/6363874/pexels-photo-6363874.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=2",
  canonicalUrl: "https://pixxelcity.com/services/celebrity",
  keywords:
    "celebrity photo studio, VIP venue rental, exclusive photography sets, private studio nagpur, influencer photoshoot venue",
};

// Enhance the service object with additional metadata
const enhancedService = {
  ...celebrityService,
  ...serviceMetadata,
  heroImage:
    "https://images.pexels.com/photos/6363874/pexels-photo-6363874.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=2",
  process: [
    {
      title: "Private Consultation",
      description:
        "We begin with a confidential discussion about your specific requirements, preferred sets, and privacy needs for the studio rental.",
    },
    {
      title: "Exclusive Booking Arrangement",
      description:
        "We schedule your session during hours when the entire studio can be reserved exclusively for you and your team, ensuring complete privacy.",
    },
    {
      title: "VIP Setup Preparation",
      description:
        "Our team prepares all selected sets, amenities, and special requests before your arrival for a seamless experience.",
    },
    {
      title: "Private Access & Security",
      description:
        "Enjoy exclusive access to our facility with enhanced privacy measures and limited staff interaction according to your preferences.",
    },
    {
      title: "Premium Support",
      description:
        "Our most experienced staff remains discreetly available throughout your booking to assist with any needs while respecting your privacy.",
    },
  ],
};
---

<ServiceDetailLayout service={enhancedService}>
  <Fragment slot="service-content">
    <h3>Exclusive Studio Rental for Public Figures & Influencers</h3>

    <p>
      For celebrities, influencers, and public figures, finding the right venue
      for photo and video content creation can be challenging. Privacy concerns,
      quality requirements, and time constraints often make conventional studios
      less than ideal.
    </p>

    <p>
      Pixxel City Studio in Nagpur offers a premium, confidential venue rental
      experience designed specifically for high-profile individuals. Our
      exclusive studio rental service combines premium sets with enhanced
      privacy measures to create an ideal environment for celebrity photoshoots
      and content creation.
    </p>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8">
      <img
        src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/6363874/pexels-photo-6363874.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=2"
        alt="Premium studio set for celebrities"
        class="rounded-lg"
      />
      <img
        src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/189333/pexels-photo-189333.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=2"
        alt="Exclusive studio venue for VIPs"
        class="rounded-lg"
      />
    </div>

    <h3>The VIP Studio Experience</h3>

    <h4>Complete Privacy & Exclusivity</h4>

    <p>
      We understand the importance of discretion. For celebrity bookings, we
      ensure exclusive use of our entire facility with private entrance options,
      restricted access, and minimal staff presence. Your security and privacy
      are our top priorities, allowing you to focus entirely on creating your
      content.
    </p>

    <h4>Premium Set Options</h4>

    <p>
      Our studio features a variety of premium set designs that provide
      sophisticated backdrops for your photoshoots. From elegant minimalist
      environments to elaborate themed settings, our versatile spaces can be
      customized to complement your personal brand and specific content needs.
    </p>

    <h4>VIP Amenities</h4>

    <p>
      Celebrity bookings include enhanced amenities such as a dedicated green
      room/lounge area, premium refreshments, spacious changing facilities, and
      any other special requests that can be accommodated. We aim to create a
      comfortable, convenient environment for you and your team.
    </p>

    <blockquote
      class="bg-primary/5 p-6 rounded-lg my-8 border-l-4 border-primary"
    >
      <p class="text-lg italic">
        "The private studio experience at Pixxel City exceeded my expectations.
        The facility was completely reserved for my team, and the sets were
        exactly what we needed for my upcoming film promotion content. The
        privacy and professionalism made the entire process smooth and
        efficient."
      </p>
      <cite class="block mt-4 font-medium">— A leading Bollywood actress</cite>
    </blockquote>

    <h3>Ideal for Various Content Needs</h3>

    <h4>Social Media Content Creation</h4>

    <p>
      For influencers and public figures who regularly create content, our
      versatile sets allow you to shoot diverse material for your digital
      platforms in one efficient session. Multiple backdrops and quick set
      changes help you build a content library in minimal time.
    </p>

    <h4>Media & Press Appearances</h4>

    <p>
      Our studio provides an ideal setting for press junkets, interview
      backdrops, or promotional photoshoots. The controlled environment ensures
      consistent, high-quality results while maintaining the privacy and
      security essential for high-profile appearances.
    </p>

    <h4>Personal Branding & Portfolio Updates</h4>

    <p>
      Keep your professional image current with regular updates in our premium
      studio environment. Our varied sets enable you to refresh your portfolio
      with diverse, high-quality images that maintain your established image
      standard.
    </p>

    <h3>Confidentiality Assurance</h3>

    <p>
      We understand the importance of discretion in all aspects of celebrity
      bookings. Our staff signs confidentiality agreements, and we implement
      strict protocols regarding your visit and any content created in our
      studio. We never disclose client information or use your name for
      promotional purposes without explicit permission.
    </p>

    <p>
      For additional security, we can arrange for private entry, limited staff
      interaction, and customized booking times that minimize the possibility of
      public awareness of your studio session.
    </p>

    <h3>Important Booking Information</h3>

    <p>
      Celebrity bookings typically use our Premium package (12 hours) to ensure
      adequate time and complete privacy. This includes exclusive use of the
      entire facility and all available sets. Please note that we provide the
      venue, sets, and premium amenities—you'll need to bring your own
      photographer and stylist team.
    </p>

    <p>
      Due to the customized nature of VIP bookings, we recommend contacting us
      well in advance through your management team or our private channels. All
      arrangements are handled with complete confidentiality from the initial
      inquiry through the booking process.
    </p>

    <h3>Book Your Exclusive Studio Session</h3>

    <p>
      For confidential inquiries about our VIP studio rental services, please
      contact us through our private line or email. Our team will work
      discreetly with you or your representatives to arrange an exclusive studio
      experience that meets your specific needs and expectations.
    </p>
  </Fragment>
</ServiceDetailLayout>
